description: If you’re wondering what’s for dinner, The Original Döner Truck has the answer. This big red truck is serving up the traditional Turkish dish that’s so delicious, with flavorful juicy meat shaved straight off from a vertical rotisserie and served to you fresh and fast. Not only is this food crazy-tasty, it’s pretty healthy for you too, so you can enjoy the goods without the guilt.Come on down to The Original Döner Truck for quite a delectable time.
name: The Original Döner Truck
